TY  - JOUR
T1  - On Some Works of Kantorovich, Koopmans and Others
AU  - Charnes, A.
AU  - Cooper, W. W.
Y1  - 1962/04/01
PY  - 1962
DA  - 1962/04/01
N1  - doi: 10.1287/mnsc.8.3.246
